{"tid":658938,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"Wound healing保持乾燥定少少濕度好？","createTime":"2018-05-09T11:38:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T18:11:13.000Z","uid":35581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"21110f0bca9743b38430c4708bbebeb23961e6b9","tid":658938,"uid":35581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T11:38:37.000Z","msg":"保持濕度會唔會易有infection?<br />\n見藥房有賣hydrocolloid 話可以保持濕度加快wound healing同少scarring. <br />\n但有無話乜情況先需要用？平時用開紗布 但又成日痴傷口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34368f8673436ac16fe5ef8b5439a0157d6a17e","tid":658938,"uid":29929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T12:56:07.000Z","msg":"少少。<br />\n<br />\n因為乾反而slow down healing process <br />\nsince formation of granulation requires water"},{"pid":"87ff649f8739f730c66b505c80136a81b0432d5f","tid":658938,"uid":29929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T12:58:18.000Z","msg":"你會定期洗傷口架嘛(normal condition ~ 3days一次)<br />\n<br />\n咁咪可以係wound healing 同 infection prevention 取平衡"},{"pid":"73736e3ea19b66de59a91caf97aad004f69945d6","tid":658938,"uid":181129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:00:00.000Z","msg":"濕但要冇菌。一發炎就麻煩起疤。兩者擇乾比較安全。"},{"pid":"d0416b3455e4f581346dee8142faa75ab56ebd59","tid":658938,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73736e3ea19b66de59a91caf97aad004f69945d6","tid":658938,"uid":181129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:00:00.000Z","msg":"濕但要冇菌。一發炎就麻煩起疤。兩者擇乾比較安全。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:08:08.000Z","msg":"無可能做到無菌架 一般wound healing都係用gauze"},{"pid":"2f7eae0f151f2bec58f29627d7572da4ac4bbd72","tid":658938,"uid":16552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0416b3455e4f581346dee8142faa75ab56ebd59","tid":658938,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73736e3ea19b66de59a91caf97aad004f69945d6","tid":658938,"uid":181129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:00:00.000Z","msg":"濕但要冇菌。一發炎就麻煩起疤。兩者擇乾比較安全。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:08:08.000Z","msg":"無可能做到無菌架 一般wound healing都係用gauze"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T18:11:13.000Z","msg":"有d gauze係有antibotics殺下d菌, <br />\n不過hydrocolloid應係冇<br />\n我習慣先用消毒藥水(或者sterile生理鹽水)洗傷口先<br />\n再用日本買既hydrocolloid膠布<br />\n呢d台灣通常叫人工皮, 香港唔知係咪叫豬油膏?<br />\n咁樣d表面d既果d傷口真係冇乜疤, 又冇咁痛<br />\n不過如果本身傷口深到入真皮, 要縫針果d就都係爭d, 會有條紅痕"}]}